@startuml
title Traffic influencing flows between OpenNESS controller and 5G Core

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam participantStyle rectangle
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor LightYellow
}
skinparam lifelineStrategy nosolid

actor "User/Admin" as UserAdmin1 at leftmost
participant "<b>OpenNESS Controller components</b>" as ONC_Comp_Container <<container>> #LightBlue [0] 
rectangle UI_CLI within ONC_Comp_Container [[UI/CLI]]
rectangle AF_Microservice within ONC_Comp_Container [[AF Microservice]] 

note right of NEF : <u><font color=black size="24">NEF\nNetwork Exposure Function </font></u>\n<color=#38761d>The Network \nexposure function provides means to expose capabilities\nto third party applications.</color>


box "#9ACD32"<b>5G Core Components</b>#Black [/]<#white>[/]
   participant NGCP_Functions<<component>>[[NGC CP Functions]][[Next Generation Control Plane functions ]]as NGCFunc  
end box 


== Get all subscribed traffic influence info ==
activate UserAdmin1
UserAdmin1 -> UI_CLI++: Request all traffic influence subscribed
deactivate UserAdmin1
UI_CLI->AF_Microservice ++:/af/v1/subscriptions : GET
AF_Microservice -->ONC_Comp_Container /3gpp-traffic-Influence/v1/{aflId}/subscriptions :GET
on call overline
group{On Call OverLine}{
	autonumber "[0]" "." "" hide footbox
	
	ONC_Comp_Container-->NGCFunc:{Open: 3rd party NGC integration with OpenNESS(NEF)}	
	deactivate ONC_Comp_Container
	note on link #lightgreen:<i>{Open: 3rd party NGC<br/>integration with<br/><b>OpenNESS(NEF)</b>}</i>
	end group
	on return underline
	group{return under line }{
		
			hide footbox
			
				return OK: traffic influence info ERROR: {400/500}
			
				
					UI_CLI<-return--OK: traffic influence info ERROR: {400/500}
					
						UserAdmin1 <- -Traffic influence details
		
						 end group



